{"word":"G4878 - συναντιλαμβάνομαι - synantilambánomai - soon-an-tee-lam-ban'-om-ahee - Help","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συναντιλαμβάνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synantilambánomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-an-tee-lam-ban'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Help</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உதவிசெய்"},{"paragraph":"to lay hold along with, to strife to obtain with others, help in obtaining"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G482 - ἀντιλαμβάνομαι - antilambánomai - an-tee-lam-ban'-om-ahee/482\">G482</a>; to <i>take</i> hold of <i>opposite together</i>, that is, <i>co-operate</i> (<i>assist</i>): - help.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G482/482\">G482</a>, <a href=\"#/G484/484\">G484</a>, <a href=\"#/G4878/4878\">G4878</a>"}]}